Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we're actually popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought our merch was pretty cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because of your weird naming sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toge-Toge rubber bands!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who wants to buy some Toge-Toge towels?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're doing better than in our Shin-Kawasaki days at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, we have some merch that's selling like hotcakes right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never getting into a bath again in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You really should. Preferably head first!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass on those.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we might be of interest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}SHIOMI MIURA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:00:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Golden Archer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Indeed. \N- I think I've heard that name somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a talent agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:44.37,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H0FFFFFF&\3c&H777777&\4c&HFFFFFF\i1\b1\fnSegoe Script\pos(1500,932)}WANDERVOGEL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, you're scouting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that is my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you are welcome to look us up online in case you have any doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you know them?\N- Yeah, they're pretty well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A few people from my school said they'd love to work with them specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They even have several bands under them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But talent agencies are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a big fan of Diamond Dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But not the way they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They lost that spark that made them special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I'm a big fan of yours in particular!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be able to make the kind of music you always did!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think this band can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time Diamond Dust was contacted by an agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we were immediately told that we'll have to change our style,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,since it doesn't fit the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And frankly, I don't think they were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact that most of the fans accepted them as they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite that, these four still want to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fully intent on going all the way, with my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't plan on letting them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be playing at the festival, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a splash at the festival, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a5}SHIOMI MIURA\NGOLDEN ARCHER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If we manage to stand out,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be easier for the agency to find us a label that can produce us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we already have a big enough fanbase, the label won't see a need for us to change our style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So this festival's gonna be like an audition for us, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you think up some lyrics for our new song?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see how it'll turn out. A song written by my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is that they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you had an idea before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyrics exist outside of us, you get what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment we write them down,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like something that was inside us takes on a life of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And who exactly died and made you the resident philosopher?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How many songs do you think I've written?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Owowowowow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I get what you're saying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, break's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Welco-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...how?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are y-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe a certain Iseri should be working part-time here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she has a shift today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Rupa-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz10.59\pos(1112,180)}Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,396)\frz10.59}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz10.59\pos(1068,448)}Mom's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(592,672)\frz10.59}I'm not surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, you could've warned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you're came crashing in here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta say, it's really nice in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know why they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you at least try talking to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking to them doesn't really work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with your grandma, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't see things the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All they do is spout nonsense all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I have to focus on the lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time until the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Our future's at stake here, I can't bother myself with this right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds to me like you're just running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, you planning to stay the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You ran away, didn't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're even bombarding me with calls at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Recipient: Muneo Iseri Sender: Nina Iseri{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did you tell them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you expect after sending them a letter like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they'll show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think they'd just accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have something to say, say it to their faces without running away all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they change the lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my apartment, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the new keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, why is everyone so damn annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We told the manager you'll be on vacation for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as a present from both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TOKYO -> KUMAMOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Tomo-chan already mentioned it to you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day of the accident, I was supposed to call my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had to stay at work for a bit longer than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd call them the next day, thinking I had all the time in the world for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a lot less time and opportunities than we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for rambling about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think they're that worried now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They never really cared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't asking for sound effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your weakness, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go and talk to them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're misunderstanding yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep down, what's really bothering you the most
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't the exams, or the bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the fact that your father didn't side with you at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's no reason to avoid them, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go and settle this. And you're banned from my place until you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The train towards Suizenji and Hikarinomori will now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TATSUTAGUCHI STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Three, two, one…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked everywhere for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Family Principles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A band?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want to make a living from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They even got scouted by an agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're basically one step away from being pros at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know how much of that is true though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You left, saying that you're going to study for college exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you started this whole thing without even telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She did tell me, partially at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you even stop to think about your poor mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go pulling that card again.\NAs if it's about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, when I left, I remember you telling me to do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told you that's exactly what I intend to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I don't mind it as long as you get into a college.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize just how much we let you get away with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to quit school, we agreed and handled all the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to go to Tokyo, we arranged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just spin the story to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I did all of that my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit school by myself, and I'm living in Tokyo by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You only got your apartment because your mother vouched for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Remind me again, who exactly is written as your guarantor in the documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re still a minor. Do you understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There are adults who are responsible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just have to do as you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend I was never bullied?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I came all this way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,hoping that maybe we could understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is what I get, right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to come with me somewhere tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to my school, aren't we? I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told them we'll be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you had things to say to me, I have things I want to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming when it's so hot outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}LETTER OF APOLOGY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s no issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been hard on you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Could we begin?\N- Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We conducted our investigation, and the student in question told us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to apologize on behalf of the school for not becoming aware of this sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s it? Are you saying the school will not take responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s not what I’m saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But according to school rules, considering this to be bullying would be a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize I'm not in a position to talk as if I've been there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but surely the school wasn't completely in the dark about-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? You are the victim here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san, about Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case she doesn't come back...what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever will be, will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you staying for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Going back already?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're serious about the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That song
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,gave me the courage I lacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,People kept telling me to grit my teeth, that it was the smart thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\i1}Letter of introspection{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So naturally, I always thought that's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I heard that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I proved that I wasn't in the wrong, I wouldn't have to suffer through it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have to constantly be afraid, and could just take the leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was no way of knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,whether I would fall into the depths of hell or fly towards the vast blue skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And that song is what let me fly in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer have solid ground to return to, and I don't need any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,back then, I really wanted to kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not actually have wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and I might just be daydreaming about flying,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but I love myself as I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say it with my head held high now. Here I am, the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But please, at least eat dinner before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, lotus root curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are we eating here?\N- Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the family principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have been a bit weird since you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad started drinking alcohol he can't even handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He was completely wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"What do you think I should do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He was saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just that worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be a famous educator,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but he still went around asking for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, your mom gave this train ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to your friends in secret, and told them to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't notice, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know our parents are clumsy, but they still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love you too, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Mom's curry always this spicy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Family Principles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\i1}Nina, 10 years old{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything is so white Everything is so slow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the answers are empty of substance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You like this song, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for always being so selfish and never listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to cut back on smoking a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm leaving. I'm leaving.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm leaving.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sing a song I wrote soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come listen to it if you have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks for the branch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're awkward, meddlesome, and irritating. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I still love them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye. See you soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for choosing to ride with us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}EMPTINESS AND CATHARSIS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss? Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my souvenir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Momoka-san wasn't sure you'd be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One more day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and she would've had me drive everyone to Kumamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She was saying she'd drive there herself if she had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit more and Rupa-san would've had to pull out all the stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you were all on board with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, she's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are definitely tears, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, she can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa-san, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmmm, can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.75,0:22:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you finish the lyrics or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, they turned out great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next up: "The Center of the World".{\i0}
